<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8182085>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. New records in Cerambycidae.A: Pirangoclytus sulphurosus (Di Iorio, 2006); B: Placosternus guttatus (Chevrolat, 1860); C: Solangebira tacuarembo (Napp & Martins, 2002); D: Exallancyla tuberculicollis (Aurivillius, 1920); E. Prosternal and mesoventral processes of P. guttatus; F: Prosternal and mesoventral processes of Megacyllene mellyi (Chevrolat, 1862) (CEIOC 17072). Scale bar: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8182085/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

